# Frontend API Configuration
# The frontend now uses relative paths for all API calls (/api)
# This works seamlessly in both development and production:
#
# Development:
#   - Vite dev server runs on http://localhost:5173
#   - Vite proxy redirects /api requests to http://localhost:8000
#
# Production:
#   - Frontend deployed at https://scopio.in
#   - Nginx routing handles /api requests to the Django backend
#   - No hardcoded URLs needed - relative paths work with any domain
#
# No environment variables are required for API configuration
